com.android.camera.gallery

Class ImageListUber

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.camera.gallery.ImageListUber
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IImageList

    public class ImageListUber
extends java.lang.Object
implements IImageList
    A union of different IImageList. This class can merge several IImageList into one list and sort them according to the timestamp (The sorting must be same as all the given lists).
